details.name: Echo Stomp
details.description: Elder Titan and his Astral Spirit both stomp the ground, damaging and knocking nearby enemy units unconscious around their locations.  The Elder Titan stomp deals physical damage, while the Spirit stomp deals magical damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Echo Stomp now causes you to become Spell Immune while channeling and for 2 additional seconds per affected enemy hero.
